---
title: Nourishing Falafel & Carrot Couscous Bowl with Garlic Sauce
description: When a wholesome and nutritious falafel dinner tastes as good as this one, it's easy to do your body a favour. Tuck in and let the refreshing carrot couscous and warm falafel take you to a state of bliss.

